HEADWORD: Territoriality
<hw>Ter`ri*to`ri*al"i*ty</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>a
pattern of behavior characterized by the marking and defense of a home
territory, exhibited by certain male animals.</def>⟦br⟧
